{"tid":1258422,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"作左隻歌送比大家 請笑納","createTime":"2019-06-26T06:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T04:02:28.000Z","uid":269389,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"863eeb18757e358553e9efb80203ca7df58e7114","tid":1258422,"uid":269389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"大家好 想因近日發生既事為香港人打氣並藉此悼念烈士。本人不材都唔識音樂方面既野及個人能力資源有限，所以膽粗粗唱作左隻歌叫「不撤不散」獻上心意。請笑納。<br />\n<br />\n喺爭取民主自由既路上或者會覺得好疲倦，但依家先係岩岩開始，不論你係勇武、和理非定中立派，希望我作既呢隻「不撤不散」令大家勿忘初心。<br />\n<br />\n共勉之，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MXaXLLkL5Qg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMXaXLLkL5Qg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=cd73957e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MXaXLLkL5Qg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"5122ebb8082a0c1a02a55ccac27df7202cfdc910","tid":1258422,"uid":229955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJn1ce0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJn1ce0.png&h=0aeb1555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n//<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/seekforg20help\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fseekforg20help&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=3a8168c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/seekforg20help</a><br />\n由於今日步行路線比較複雜，所以我地會用呢個頻道keep住update遊行隊伍去到咩位置，方便想中途加入既人搵到我地。所以<span style=\"color: gold;\">希望大家可以幫手share呢條Channel出去，感謝！</span><br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n2LmYZa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn2LmYZa.png&h=1855d90a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前立法局主席黃宏發踢爆：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">議事規則得撤回 押後 postpone or withdraw</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇暫緩</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/PrrEBU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/PrrEBU</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">(懶既直接係最底copy) </span></span></div><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a74bba05349421dc429e5bd53487dfb283d9262","tid":1258422,"uid":61679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"真心作得幾好<br />\n支持<br />\nMixing同埋填詞都係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"5df7b6af73a32ec60644584cabc65d5b40c95d27","tid":1258422,"uid":269389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a74bba05349421dc429e5bd53487dfb283d9262","tid":1258422,"uid":61679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"真心作得幾好<br />\n支持<br />\nMixing同埋填詞都係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"一人一手包辦<br />\n<br />\n脷伸: 唔識音樂野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}